Class CityList

  • java.lang.Object
    • CityList

  • public class CityList
extends java.lang.Object
    The CityList class creates a list of cities with arrays of their names, whether they've been visited, the number of cities in the array and their adjacent cities. MAX_CITIES sets the maximum amount of cities. cityNames holds an array of city names. visited holds flags for whether the city at that particular index has been visited. manyItems stores the amount of cities currently in the list. adjacentCities holds an array of linked lists that stores data on citys' available destinations.
    Author:
    Sam
